Bitcoin's market price (set by the marginal buyer/seller * supply) is below its realized price (price last paid per coin * supply). Realized price is a proxy for the cost basis of the market.

Being below realized price (green zone) means the mkt is underwater in aggregate. https://t.co/2VIUeVdueb
